info.author: Alexander Duryagin
info.description:
This package provides python interface to nagios configuration, objects and
status files. It parses main config, config files for nagios objects (hosts,
services, ...) and status file to retrieve full picture, it is able to change
and create objects, which then may be saved.

Also it provides simplified api for easier information retrieval.

Development continues, so please look at git for updated and bug-fixed version.
info.name: python-nagdata
info.summary: Python interface to Nagios object and status files
info.html_description:
This package provides python interface to nagios configuration, objects and status files. It parses main config, config files for nagios objects (hosts, services, …) and status file to retrieve full picture, it is able to change and create objects, which then may be saved.

Also it provides simplified api for easier information retrieval.

Development continues, so please look at git for updated and bug-fixed version.
